(68, 1, '2014-06-23 22:05:27', '2014-06-23 22:05:27', 'The lovely Wieting Theater serves as the primary venue for Green Gravel. The Wieting has brought fine arts ranging from live opera to 3D movies to the Toledo region since 1912. This 300-seat balcony-tiered gem has been restored and maintained by the community, showcasing the tireless work and cultural heritage of the people of Toledo. We’re honored to host our event here and can’t wait to share this completely unique live, hilarious experience with you!', 'The Weiting Theatre', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-weiting-theatre', '', '', '2014-06-29 21:28:54', '2014-06-29 21:28:54', '', 0, 'http://localhost/NewGravel/?post_type=venues&#038;p=68', 0, 'venues', '', 0),
